# The reference knowledge base ships with the app (read-only, regenerable via
# `python knowledge_base/scraper.py`). It is committed so the Hugging Face Space
# needs no ingest/scrape at runtime. To exclude it from version control instead,
# re-add the two lines below and rebuild it on the host:
#   knowledge_base/lancedb_data/
#   knowledge_base/sources/reference_images/
